Name: Vega
Description: One of the Fixers. Adept at taking control of enemy units. Can use Dominate. Can be upgraded to be a Detector.**Can attack ground and air units**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Stuns all enemies and deals 1000 damage over 5 seconds in a large area.
Root.Name: Barrage

Root.Tooltip: Calls down a Nuclear Strike at a target location. Nukes take 3 seconds to land, but they deal up to 1000 damage in a large area.
Root.Name: Big Red Button

Root.Tooltip: Temporarily take control of target enemy unit and increases its damage by 50.0%. Dominated units self-destruct after 240 seconds. Holds up to 3 charges.
Root.Name: Dominate

Root.Tooltip: Temporarily take control of target enemy unit and increases its damage by 50.0%. Dominated units self-destruct after 240 seconds. Holds up to 3 charges.
Root.Name: Dominate

Root.Tooltip: This upgrade unlocks at Commander Level 14.
Root.Name: Type-88 Persuader

Root.Tooltip: Increases the duration of Dominate by 200%.
Root.Name: Type-88 Persuader

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Enemy units in an area around a dominated unit will attack each other for 10 seconds.
Root.Name: Neural Disruption Device

Root.Tooltip: Brings up to 5 enemy air units to the ground, allowing units to attack them as if they were ground units.
Root.Name: Psi Projector

Root.Tooltip: Dominate fully restores the target's life, shields, and energy and increases its attack speed by 75%.
Root.Name: Moebius Psionic Motivator
